-- Black Bought Munch’s `Scream' for About $120 Million, WSJ Says
-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 2012-07-11T21:17:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-11/black-bought-munch-s-scream-for-about-120-million-wsj-says.html
Leon Black , chairman and founder of
Apollo Global Management LLC, bought Edvard Munch’s “The
Scream” in a  Sotheby’s (BID)  Inc. auction for about $120 million, the
Wall Street Journal reported on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
